

=Bio=

"Multi-disciplinar researcher: water, data, socio-ecological systems, societal metabolism, openknowledge&science, P2P. Interested in interactions, socioecological change processes and meeting points between scales, disciplines and perceptions.

My lenses: complex systems. My passion: social movements and politics. Indignada. Once, activist #15M in Real Democracry Now and some of its evolutions.

This blog aims at science dissemination in my fields of work: a meeting point between ecological economics and water management. In general I will write in English scientific posts and in Spanish dissemination and discussion issues of Spanish environmental management."
